divs: sighting detailsi was laying down on a lawn chair and looking at the stars fully awake, this thing flew along above me at something like 1000 feet or more. it circled above me 3 or 4 times, gaining altitude as it did until it disappeared out of site. it looked like a shoe heel from a man���s hard sole shoe. it had a rounded end and a squared end and it had 4 round dimples or impressions evenly spaced on the bottom in a square pattern. i could not tell how thick it was, i could only see the bottom and the leading round edge. it didn't look very thick. it wasn't really easy to see. it had no lights and a dull dark color the only thing making it visible was the ground lighting reflecting off of it. from my vantage point it was about 6 inches long from rounded end to the square end and 5 inches across the other way. it was oriented with the round end going first. speed, it covered about 1\4 of the sky in about 15 seconds. it was travelling west from lake ontario.
